{"tid":2332012,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃之鋒再上庭 祝大家「聖誕新年快樂」","createTime":"2020-12-19T09:17:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T09:56:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"158b93454a6016380eb01dd98a4494cd6e9e2586","tid":2332012,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T09:17:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201219/2CKDLOVJQRFAHHMV3PW4SHAK6I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201219%2F2CKDLOVJQRFAHHMV3PW4SHAK6I%2F&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWAg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=172729af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201219%2F2CKDLOVJQRFAHHMV3PW4SHAK6I%2F&h=a50d8762\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201219/2CKDLOVJQRFAHHMV3PW4SHAK6I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒再上庭 祝大家「聖誕新年快樂」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pFAjdYJgFv7uvyhXvYwCp9auoKw=/705x397/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AKMGUKGLF5GATBWXRT2F7X6ZTY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpFAjdYJgFv7uvyhXvYwCp9auoKw%3D%2F705x397%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAKMGUKGLF5GATBWXRT2F7X6ZTY.jpg&h=f4f1b1b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黃之鋒昨被押往東區法院應訊，登上囚車前舉起雙手展示手銬。<br />\n<br />\n【未經批准集結案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒及社運人士古思堯。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n案件押下月訊<br />\n<br />\n現時正因去年6.21包圍警總案服刑的黃之鋒，昨日早上在荔枝角收押所被鎖上手銬，由懲教人員帶上囚車，前往東區法院應訊。<br />\n<br />\n辯方申請押後答辯，等待終審法院下周一就蒙面法作出的終極裁決，以給予被告法律意見。主任裁判官錢禮因應要求，將案件押後至明年1月29日再訊。黃之鋒昨被押送上庭應訊，身穿黑色大褸的他，多次凝視着公眾席，似乎精神不俗。<span class=\"orange\">他在離開法庭時向旁聽席報以微笑說道：「大家聖誕、新年快樂。」大批人士在旁聽席高舉雙手，高呼「之鋒，加油！」及「撐住呀！」</span><br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒因去年6月21日參與包圍警察總部，被控煽惑、組織及參與未經批准集結等罪名，最終在本月初被重判入獄13個半月，現正服刑。判刑當日，黃之鋒步入囚室前曾大叫：「知道好難捱，但撐住呀！」<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒（23歲）與<span class=\"orange\">古思堯（74歲）</span>同樣被控以參與未經批准集結罪，指他們去年10月5日在港犯案。黃之鋒另外被控在未經批准集結中使用蒙面物品，<span class=\"orange\">指他使用耳掛式口罩</span>。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC2097/20"},{"pid":"716dc36a4c69bec43b16f5d20f5d47f3c0d3a3cc","tid":2332012,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T09:29:05.000Z","msg":"祝新居出入平安"},{"pid":"b4c81f96337e288624fcc0744635e7093945b930","tid":2332012,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T09:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e708debd74edd4819204899fa1886917629384b","tid":2332012,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T09:56:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}